{"tid":892753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網上尋人 揭開一段香港60年代純愛故事","createTime":"2018-11-07T06:24:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T02:07:58.000Z","uid":184679,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2f57121e1a74f3415ba6db6b8ba26dc06e9c918e","tid":892753,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T06:24:55.000Z","msg":"尋人故事，多數係搵親人。<br />\n<br />\n呢個post想搵嘅，係那些年的心動對象&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n一位英國華僑Selina Wong喺facebook一個分享香港60年代事物嘅群組出post，<br />\n<br />\n想幫媽媽搵返一位老朋友。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n故事要由1968年講起。<br />\n<br />\n嗰年，Selina嘅媽媽Nancy 20歲，芳華正茂，喺尖沙咀加拿芬道麗琪餅店工作。<br />\n<br />\n有位叫Danny嘅年青人，每日都會去呢間餅店幫襯。<br />\n<br />\n如是者過咗半年。<br />\n<br />\n有次Danny仲揸電單車接放工，送Nancy返上水嘅屋企。<br />\n<br />\n由尖沙咀去上水！仲要係幾十年前，冇吐露港公路，獅子山隧道都係剛剛通車&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n不過，呢個時候Nancy要移民英國，<br />\n<br />\nDanny得知後寫咗一封簡單而深情嘅表白信俾Nancy。<br />\n<br />\n故事暫告一段落。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n事隔50年，Nancy嘅女兒代媽媽喺網上尋找Danny，<br />\n<br />\n想知道呢位當年騎著電單車嘅青年，而家嘅下落。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n根據原post，Danny 姓禢，生於1949年。<br />\n<br />\n呢個姓氏唔算普遍，有冇朋友嘅屋企人，<br />\n<br />\n年約70歲，後生時揸過電單車？<br />\n<br />\n有的話，請你入呢個post(<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/HK60s/permalink/10155660269611712/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2FHK60s%2Fpermalink%2F10155660269611712%2F&d=8pkJm4AEPJNnEtdN9MQM%2BSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=9f40ab88\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/HK60s/permalink/10155660269611712/</a>)同Selina聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E5%B0%8B%E4%BA%BA-%E6%8F%AD%E9%96%8B-%E6%AE%B5%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF60%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3%E7%B4%94%E6%84%9B%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B-024550985.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%25B0%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E6%258F%25AD%25E9%2596%258B-%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF60%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E7%25B4%2594%25E6%2584%259B%25E6%2595%2585%25E4%25BA%258B-024550985.html&d=8pkJm4AEPJNnEtdN9MQM%2BSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=ee919d16\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E5%B0%8B%E4%BA%BA-%E6%8F%AD%E9%96%8B-%E6%AE%B5%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF60%E5%B9%B4%E4%BB%A3%E7%B4%94%E6%84%9B%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B-024550985.html</a>"},{"pid":"927b29c4ccda169f7af9b6922e97fe9fb525d5e5","tid":892753,"uid":201834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T06:26:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f8c870a046df1e04ea12e87b25a885a245a6217e","tid":892753,"uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T06:28:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/jHTsbFTGK2o/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FjHTsbFTGK2o%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=9685d946&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"450702bed2e0fe1497dec866a870cc05a9adcea8","tid":892753,"uid":34884,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T06:31:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uGxjndp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuGxjndp.png&h=74ddba50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e235e2790a7d2966bcd3a8109937d68e8d52d5e4","tid":892753,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T06:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea69662be9c04076682462e50c2c7934deab9ff","tid":892753,"uid":193436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T07:00:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"edfd77f2eb37f1770255fc83b25e3d1c2edb1e41","tid":892753,"uid":2772,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"cited